{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/adjust-the-height-of-an-element-using-the-height-property","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Podesite visinu elementa koristeći height svojstvo","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Možete postaviti visinu elementa koristeći <code>height</code> svojstvo u CSS, slično kao <code>width</code> svojstvo. Evo primera koji menja visinu slike na 20px:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">img {\n  height: 20px;\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"587d7791367417b2b2512ab5","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodajte <code>height</code> svojstvo na <code>h4</code> element i postavite ga na 25px.</p>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Možda ćete morati da zumirate na 100% kako biste prošli izazov.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cEDaDTN","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301034,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/adjust-the-height-of-an-element-using-the-height-property"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  h4 {\n    text-align: center;\n\n  }\n  p {\n    text-align: justify;\n  }\n  .links {\n    margin-right: 20px;\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n  .fullCard {\n    width: 245px;\n    border: 1px solid #ccc;\n    border-radius: 5px;\n    margin: 10px 5px;\n    padding: 4px;\n  }\n  .cardContent {\n    padding: 10px;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"fullCard\">\n  <div class=\"cardContent\">\n    <div class=\"cardText\">\n      <h4>Google</h4>\n      <p>Google was founded by Larry Page and Sergey Brin while they were Ph.D. students at Stanford University.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"cardLinks\">\n      <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Larry_Page\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"links\">Larry Page</a>\n      <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sergey_Brin\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"links\">Sergey Brin</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vaš kod treba da postavi <code>height</code> svojstvo <code>h4</code> elementa na vrednost od 25 piksela.</p>","testString":"const spaceFreeText = document.querySelector(\"style:not(.fcc-hide-header)\")?.textContent?.replace(/\\s/g, ''); \nconst h4Element = document.querySelector('h4');\nassert.equal(Math.round(h4Element?.getBoundingClientRect()?.height),25);\nassert.match(spaceFreeText,/h4{\\S*height:25px(;\\S*}|})/);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#applied-visual-design","dashedName":"adjust-the-height-of-an-element-using-the-height-property","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"applied-visual-design","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-the-strong-tag-to-make-text-bold","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/adjust-the-width-of-an-element-using-the-width-property","id":"587d7791367417b2b2512ab5","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\n  .balls {\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    position: fixed;\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    top: 60%;\n    animation-name: jump;\n    animation-duration: 2s;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n  #red {\n    background: red;\n    left: 25%;\n    animation-ti